	   <tr><td colspan=2>need to figure what race to play IKY or Troll help, like the regen of both troll stronger , iky better at magic any ideas?????<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
